  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the feasibility (acceptability) of a consultation dedicated to
      informing women about their risk of breast cancer and the screening methods recommended for
      them according to the recommendations in force during a routine consultation at a general
      practitioner, a gynecologist or a radiologist.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
